{
  "decision_conditions": [
    "Reason : 1 - The scheme fails to demonstrate that the proposed accommodation would meet identified local need for a residential care home and no evidence has been provided to demonstrate that nomination arrangements have been agreed with the Council. The proposal is therefore contrary to Local Plan Policy SC8.",
    "Reason : 2 - The scheme has failed to demonstrate how the proposed development will avoid any adverse impact on the amenity of neighbouring residents due to the increased comings and goings expected from the shift-based staffing leading to greater noise, disturbances, parking and traffic stress within the neighbourhood. This proposal is therefore contrary to Local Plan Policies CC2, EC2 and EQ5.",
    "Reason : 3 - The proposal does not make adequate arrangements for refuse and recycling, or car and cycle parking and fails to demonstrate that it would not prejudice the safe and efficient operation of the Local Transport Network, this would be contrary to London Plan Policies T5, T6 and T6.1, and Local Plan Policies EC2 and EQ7."
  ],
